game.name: Panda Commander
game.description:
It is time to sit on a plane and have a wonderful yet challenging ride high in the sky with your favourite panda! But, the problem is that panda does know how to operate a plane in a sky where the number of enemies is very high. Would you be able to help him face off the enemies in a great battle in the air? If yes, join Panda Commander Air Combat game and be prepared to become a fighter pilot in the highly challenging air battle. 
Fly awesome jet airplanes like a pro pilot and prove the world that you are a true fighter whether it is road or a sky! Be careful and try to destroy as many enemies as you can to score high in this brand new action game! These invader planes will try to occupy the territory of your favourite Panda. You have to help your true friend by destroying the rivals. Dodge the bullets of your enemies by moving the plane!
Do not forget to collect the stars that you see in the sky. Heal your health by just grabbing the extra life in this HTML5 shooting game! Fight hard and try to survive until you reach the final boss in each level! Common boys! We know that you have the guts to face different types of enemies in this one of the greatest air war games. Get the combos to boost your score! Good luck to survive for as long as possible!
